rows.label: qev031101_MSG0001
rows.name:
Earth alien! You are BLADE? I have request.
But first I have question.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0002
rows.name:
Do you love trees? Respect trees?
Feel life-pulse inside them?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0010
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0011
rows.name: Claim that you believe all nature should be respected.

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0020
rows.name: Deny

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that trees are just materials waiting to be harvested.

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0003
rows.name: I sense you speak truth. I will trust you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0004
rows.name: ...Then begone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0005
rows.name:
I have seed of hope. I protect it with my life.
I cannot trust it to such as you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0006
rows.name: I am Naza Tenpanzi. Protector of Great Tree.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0007
rows.name: You must help me raise Great Tree from seed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0008
rows.name: First you must accept. Then I will explain all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0009
rows.name:
I defend this seed with my life. I cannot expose it to
danger. We must keep its secret safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0010
rows.name:
It is good I spoke to you. Some Earth aliens are
unworthy of trust. Speaking to you was gamble.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0030
rows.name: Worry

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0031
rows.name: Ask Naza if she is in danger.

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0040
rows.name: Inquire

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0041
rows.name: Ask Naza about the Great Tree.

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0011
rows.name:
I kept this seed safe from Ganglion.
It put me in much danger.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0012
rows.name:
But that does not matter. I do not matter.
Only Great Tree matters.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0013
rows.name:
Ganglion raided our home. Killed many.
Burned trees that were host to Old Ones.
So I took action...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0014
rows.name:
I buried seed of Great Tree within my own flesh.
Then survived.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0015
rows.name: All so Great Trees might take root in this land.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0016
rows.name:
Seed must be planted in soil.
Then my task is done.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0017
rows.name:
Great Trees are host to Old Ones.
Old Ones watch over members of clan.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0018
rows.name: Clans tend Great Trees in return.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0019
rows.name:
But Ganglion put Great Trees to flame.
Tried to crush our resolve.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0020
rows.name:
Some protectors resisted. They met death.
Some relented. They burned Great Trees themselves.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0021
rows.name:
I did neither. I buried last seed within my flesh.
Then stayed out of sight. Stayed alive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0022
rows.name:
Journey has been long. But it is almost over.
Now I must entrust seed to soil.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0023
rows.name:
But this land is different from our home.
I fear seed will not grow. So I seek aid from others.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0024
rows.name:
You must find someone who knows of plants.
Ask how to grow trees on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0050
rows.name: Accept

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0051
rows.name: Tell Naza that you will do it.

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0060
rows.name: Query

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0061
rows.name: Ask if Naza has any leads on possible tree experts.

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0025
rows.name:
Some Prone have forgotten trees.
It is good you do not.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0026
rows.name:
We need protection of Old Ones in this land.
And Old Ones need Great Trees.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0027
rows.name:
I expect Earth aliens are no different. You would also
feel weak if something dear was stolen from you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0028
rows.name: I hear Ma-non are wise. Also Orphe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0029
rows.name:
And you are wise as well, Earth alien.
I trust you will find help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0030
rows.name: Lives of all Prone depend on future of this seed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0031
rows.name:
Please find wise person, Earth alien.
Teach us how to grow Great Trees on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0032
rows.name: If you need tools, I ask that you find them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0033
rows.name: Only single seed remains. We must not fail to raise it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0034
rows.name:
Professor taught me how to grow trees.
We need gnarlbranch sap.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0035
rows.name: Go to Divine Roost. Gather sap there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0036
rows.name:
Orphean professor taught me many things.
Gnarlbranch sap will make Great Tree grow strong.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0037
rows.name: Do you have any?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0038
rows.name: Will this really work?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0039
rows.name:
It should, but I only have a 99.86 percent certainty.
However, those are still most excellent odds when it
comes to botanical growth factors.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0040
rows.name: Orphean's words are difficult. But he seems good.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0041
rows.name: Can I trust what professor says?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0070
rows.name: Confirm

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0071
rows.name: Tell Naza that Mon'barac is trustworthy.

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0080
rows.name: Hesitate

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0081
rows.name: Say that Mon'barac seems a bit suspicious.

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0042
rows.name:
Yes. He accepts our problem as if it were his.
This is good sign.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0043
rows.name:
So be it. I will use gnarlbranch sap.
I will attempt to grow Great Tree.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0044
rows.name: Seed is precious. It cannot be wasted on lies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0045
rows.name:
If professor is lying, he will pay.
I will make sure he never walks again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0046
rows.name:
I assure you, the chances of that are nonexistent.
I'd even go so far as to say less than nonexistent,
were such a thing scientifically possible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0047
rows.name:
So be it. I will use gnarlbranch sap.
I will attempt to grow Great Tree.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0048
rows.name: Is this right, Professor?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0049
rows.name:
Yes, your application was indeed correct.
You need not wait long. It should sprout presently.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0050
rows.name: Amazing! It will be mighty Great Tree by tomorrow![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0051
rows.name: Old Ones will be reborn here in New LA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0052
rows.name:
Hmm, yes. It is a curious species indeed.
...And now for the tasting![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0053
rows.name: WHAAAAT?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0054
rows.name:
Trees are always best when eaten as tender saplings.
So fresh and green. Do you not you agree?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0090
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0091
rows.name: Nod vigorously.

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0100
rows.name: Backpedal

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0101
rows.name:
Suggest that Mon'barac apologize
before Naza breaks his legs.

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0056
rows.name:
Now THAT was an exotic delicacy.
Much appreciation for the fine meal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0057
rows.name:
Apologize? As in, express contrition? I am confused.
How does such a thing apply here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0058
rows.name:
YOU! What did you do?!
How could you eat Great Tree?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0059
rows.name:
Plants exist as food. They hold no other purpose.
...Mmm, you still seem quite perturbed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0060
rows.name: Oh! How rude of me! Were you also hungry?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0061
rows.name: Grk! GWAAAAAAUGH![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0062
rows.name:
...Ah, I see. You believe that a divine being resides
within that tree of yours.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0063
rows.name:
Well, that makes senseâ€”except for the part where it is
nonsense. If I may, as a research botanist, I have
studied a vast and varied number of tree species.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0064
rows.name:
Yet not one of them has housed anything even remotely
classifiable as a god. This is a simple fact.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0065
rows.name:
We of Tree Clan believe we meet Old Ones in our
final moments...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0066
rows.name:
So I will prove you are wrong about Old Ones
when I MURDER YOU![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0067
rows.name:
Augh! B-but my Ovah insists that this is not yet the
proper time for me to perish![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0068
rows.name:
You there! Human! Do you not think you ought to
intervene before this becomes an actual tragedy?
I simply cannot imagine why this Prone is so angry![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0110
rows.name: Explain to Mon'barac

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0111
rows.name: Thoroughly explain Mon'barac's mistake to him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_JNK0120
rows.name: Convince Naza

rows.label: qev031101_SEL0121
rows.name: Attempt to talk down the enraged Naza.

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0069
rows.name:
...So her regard for the divinity of that tree is
equivalent to the way we view our Ovah?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0070
rows.name: A most thorough explanation. Thank you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0071
rows.name:
Seeds were passed down through generations.
Inherited from earliest ancestors. It was last one left.
AND HE ATE IT![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0072
rows.name: No talk! No calm! This is unforgivable![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0073
rows.name:
Inherited from your ancestors, you say?
Is it perhaps something akin to our Ovah, then?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0074
rows.name: I think I more firmly grasp the situation now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0075
rows.name: I fear I have committed a most egregious affront.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0076
rows.name: I beg your pardon. I will revive your tree at once.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0077
rows.name: You...can do that?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0078
rows.name:
That is my profession. In consuming your tree,
I have analyzed its composition. Given the materials,
synthesizing a new instance is really quite simple.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0079
rows.name: I only need four zesian fleawort and a longevity bough.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0080
rows.name:
If you procure those, I can restore your Great Tree
with a 99.12 percent chance of perfect fidelity.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0081
rows.name:
Please, Earth alien. Find zisean fleawort and
longevity bough.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0082
rows.name:
We will soon know if he speaks truth.
If so, I forgive him. If not, I KILL HIM![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0083
rows.name: Orphean stare at me while ago.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0084
rows.name: It was unsettling. He may still be nearby.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev031101_MSG0085
rows.name: Perhaps chill I feel is message from Old Ones.[ST:wait ]
